# coord-wright — project registry.
#
# Copy this file to `projects.txt` (same directory) and list the ABSOLUTE
# path of each repository the coord workers should run for, one per line.
# Lines starting with `#` are comments. Re-run ./install.sh after editing.
#
# An empty/all-commented registry is valid — the workers simply have nothing
# to run for until you add a path.
#
# Example (replace with your own absolute paths):
#   /Users/you/Projects/my-app
#   /Users/you/Projects/another-service
